'Kecelakaan Atharva!
Kematian Dhairya!'

00:20:50.240 --> 00:20:51.640 line:20%
'Kamu bertanggung
jawab atas segalanya!'

00:20:52.000 --> 00:20:53.440 line:20%
"Terlambat, Imlie."

00:20:53.600 --> 00:20:57.960 line:20%
'Siapa yang akan mempercayaimu sekarang?
